**Trailing commas** are NOT allowed in standard JSON. Remove the last comma before a closing `}` or `]`.

```
// NOT supported in standard JSON
{"_comment": "Use this workaround"}
```
JSON does not support comments. Use JSONC (JSON with Comments) in editors, or add `_comment` keys.

A **media query** applies styles conditionally based on device characteristics.
```css
@media (max-width: 768px) { ... }
```

CSS **animations** gradually change element styles using keyframes.
```css
@keyframes name { from { } to { } }
```

**@import** brings in external stylesheets or modules.
```css
@import url("styles.css");
```
